Package: debian-control-center
Version: 2.3
Section: admin
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Gabriel Elias <gabriel.aquino86@gmail.com>
Depends: python3, python3-pyqt6 | python3-pyqt5, polkitd, pkexec, x-terminal-emulator,
 synaptic, gparted, hardinfo | hardinfo2, calamares, deb-gview, gkdebconf,
 dconf-editor, galternatives, nm-connection-editor, system-config-printer,
 ufw, gufw, firetools, timeshift, kate, lxqt-admin, lxqt-admin-l10n, gdebi
Description: Debian Control Center
 A Qt-based control center for Debian. Provides access to system
 administration tools such as Synaptic, GParted, Hardinfo, Calamares,
 GKDebconf, APT maintenance commands, .deb inspection utilities,
 service management, and configuration file editing.
 This version uses Qt Widgets and does not require QML or QtQuick.
